## Require (verb-specific)

- **(R-R1)** Ribozyme output schema = RNA spec (sequence + 2D/3D structure + predicted k_cat/K_M + 4-state ladder). **Canonical contract**: `ribozyme/spec/ribozyme_output_v1.schema.json` (`raw_77_ribozyme_design_v1`, lands cycle 25 §STALLED draft). v1 fields: `sequence.full` + `sequence.catalytic_core` (12-nt) + `structure_2d.dot_bracket` (stub-allowed pending Nussinov/Zuker inline) + `structure_3d_ref` (stub-allowed; J₂=24 TS pose tagged) + `predicted_kinetics` (k_cat / K_M / Eigen-Hammes margin) + `reaction_ladder` (4-state, τ(6)=4) + `n6_invariant` + optional `off_target_screen`. Cycle 24 MVP rows continue under sister schema `raw_77_ribozyme_kinetics_v1` (kinetics-only); cycle-26 stretch = inline MFE solver port to retire the `stub` allowance.
- **(R-R2)** Sister-axis 분담 (C0a 결과 2026-05-05 — F-RB-5 **PASS WITH MITIGATION**): hexa-bio RIBOZYME = catalytic-RNA **architectural primitive** (active-site σ(6)=12 core residues, τ(6)=4 reaction states, k_cat/K_M Eigen-Hammes diffusion ceiling, in-silico chemical-kinetics simulation L0-L4); `life/crispr-gene-editing/` = Cas9-sgRNA **system integration** + clinical delivery (downstream, no genus collision); `life/synbio/` = **in-vitro selection / SELEX** library construction + metabolic-chassis embedding. **Formalised boundary (RIBOZYME ↔ synbio/SELEX, lands §STALLED draft 2026-05-06):**
  - **Design-stage (RIBOZYME owner)**: in-silico sequence proposal, σ(6)=12 catalytic-core annotation, k_cat/K_M Eigen-Hammes margin estimate, 4-state ladder simulation (L0–L4 of n6 lattice). Output = registry row schemas `raw_77_ribozyme_kinetics_v1` (cycle 24 MVP) + `raw_77_ribozyme_design_v1` (R-R1 contract; sequence + rate constants + structural-grade tag).
  - **Selection-stage (synbio/SELEX owner, out-of-repo)**: wet-lab library construction, in-vitro round-by-round enrichment, catalytic-activity assay, hit deconvolution. Routes to L9 application layer.
  - **Handshake artefact**: registry SA-row schema (proposed `raw_77_ribozyme_selex_handoff_v0` — TBD cycle 26 if `life/synbio/` repo materialises). Until repo exists, the synbio reference is **declarative only** (R-R2 mitigation under F-RB-5 PASS WITH MITIGATION; no live cross-repo dependency).
- **(R-R3)** Meta `.roadmap.hexa_bio` §E (R1-R8) 전 도메인 Require 상속

