- **[UNDEFINED] F-RB-1 / F-RB-3 sub-falsifiers (lines 64, 68)** — deadline / 본문 / interim checkpoint 부재 (open-ended). **Resolution:** 정식 등록 또는 abandon 결정. [LANDED 2026-05-06 — sub-falsifiers F-RB-1-genus / F-RB-1-b / F-RB-1-c + F-RB-3-diffusion-limit / F-RB-3-b / F-RB-3-c integrated into "Sub-falsifier scaffolding" subsection of Falsifier preregister with 2026-09-28 deadline. Draft retained below.]
